3. **All channels affected equally**: Web, mobile app, and in-store purchases all show zero in the baseline window — this isn't channel-specific.
4. **Both product categories (Apparel and Jewelry)** show the same 14-day = 7-day pattern, ruling out a category-specific collapse.

